=Love Formula=
("Devil Young Master, Don't Mess With Me" )

13
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:40,820
=Episode 4=

14
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:42,040
Come on. Tell me.

15
00:01:42,112 --> 00:01:43,320
How has everyone been

16
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,320
while I was gone?

17
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,880
