18
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,560
But lately, we've met

19
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,920
someone pretty interesting.

20
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:50,760
Yeah? Who?

21
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,920
Just someone totally irrelevant.

22
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,200
Han Yansheng!

23
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,520
That's her.

24
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:05,080
Just help me sign
the authorization form.

25
00:02:05,155 --> 00:02:07,488
Starting the Rock Climbing Club
really matters to me.

26
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,600
This is a private party. Please leave.

27
00:02:11,711 --> 00:02:12,800
(Club Authorization Application)

28
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,688
As soon as you sign,
I'll leave right away.

29
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,320
So you mean

30
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,933
if I don't sign, you're not leaving?

31
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:26,760
Sheng.

32
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,520
You should be nicer
when you talk to girls.

33
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,520
Hi, I'm Gu Entong.

34
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,360
I was

35
00:02:33,392 --> 00:02:35,360
in the same class as Sheng and Monkey.

36
00:02:35,511 --> 00:02:37,222
I just got back
from an exchange program.

37
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:40,360
Nice to meet you.

38
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,840
Hi, Entong. I'm Jian Dan.

39
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:45,120
Jian Dan?

40
00:02:46,585 --> 00:02:48,520
Aren't you the one on the forum

41
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:51,720
who pushed Sheng into the water?

42
00:02:58,480 --> 00:03:00,360
You're even cuter in person
than in photos.

43
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,560
Thanks.

44
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,440
Let's not just stand here. Come on in.

45
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,120
Come on.

46
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:14,080
Come in. Let's go.

47
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,960
Let's all go in together.

48
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,210
I brought gifts for everyone.

49
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,320
Come on.

50
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,520
I even

51
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,440
got a gift for each one of you.

52
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:36,720
Here.

53
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,311
Sheng.

54
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:41,400
This is a sliding number puzzle,
like Huarong Road.

55
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,880
It might be super easy for you,

56
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,680
but it can help you speed up

57
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,720
your problem-solving.

58
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:47,760
Give it a try.

59
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,444
Thanks.

60
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,160
Monkey, I got you something too.

61
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,080
What is it?

62
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:59,160
My favorite flavor!

63
00:03:59,218 --> 00:03:59,840
I know.

64
00:03:59,974 --> 00:04:02,040
Entong, you're way too thoughtful.

65
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:07,080
This is the figurine
Yuan Sen's been dying to get.

66
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,720
Help me pass it to him, will you?

67
00:04:08,767 --> 00:04:11,440
See? You always think of everything.

68
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,640
I'll thank you on his behalf.

69
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:15,429
Don't mention it.
I'm not as good as you make me sound.

70
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,760
Shi.

71
00:04:21,722 --> 00:04:23,355
(Hacker Defense Handbook)
This one's for you.

72
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:25,000
You remembered my wishlist!

73
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,000
Of course.

74
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,560
I remember everything you've said.

75
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,632
Jian Dan...

76
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,880
I didn't expect to run into you today.

77
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,333
I didn't prepare a gift for you.

78
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,120
It's okay. I don't need one.

79
00:04:45,843 --> 00:04:47,269
That won't do.

80
00:04:47,377 --> 00:04:48,960
You ran over here in such a rush, right?

81
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,280
Your bangs are a little messy.

82
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,920
I just remembered I have

83
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,400
a brand-new hair clip in my bag.

84
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,720
- It's okay.
- Look.

85
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,960
I think it suits you.

86
00:04:57,218 --> 00:04:58,192
Try it on.

87
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,160
Here.

88
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,000
All done.

89
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,080
Guys, look.

90
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,200
Isn't she super cute?

91
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,560
It really is cute.

92
00:05:10,577 --> 00:05:12,860
Jian Dan, I think you should
try this hairstyle more often.

93
00:05:12,860 --> 00:05:13,750
It's seriously so cute.

94
00:05:13,755 --> 00:05:15,760
I think so too.
You look great, Jian Dan.

95
00:05:16,311 --> 00:05:17,640
Did you finish your enrollment?

96
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,760
Yeah, all done.

97
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,760
I just need to check in
with the music department.

98
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,680
It's about time.

99
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,640
I should get going now.

100
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,840
I'll catch you later.

101
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,320
Okay.

102
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:28,840
Bye, Entong.

103
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,120
Alright, bye, Jian Dan.

104
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:30,800
Bye.

105
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:31,240
Bye.

106
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,110
- Bye.
- Stay safe.

107
00:05:32,111 --> 00:05:32,822
Bye, Jian Dan.

108
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,240
Entong.

109
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,720
Entong, wait a second.

110
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,720
Jian Dan.

111
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:58,400
What is it?

112
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:00,960
Your hair clip.

113
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,440
I told you, it's a gift.

114
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:08,511
I don't think I should accept
a gift from you for no reason.

115
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,360
Alright then, I'll take it back.

116
00:06:12,163 --> 00:06:13,320
Well, I'm off, Entong.

117
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:13,720
Okay.

118
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,240
Bye.

119
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,320
Bye.

120
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,640
About the Rock Climbing Club...

121
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,840
I'd still like to talk to you.

122
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,520
Move. There's nothing to talk about.

123
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:44,680
At least tell me

124
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,088
why you won't sign it.

125
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,088
Have you ever gone climbing?

126
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,374
Do you know any techniques?

127
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:54,080
Not yet, at the moment.

128
00:06:54,963 --> 00:06:55,760
But I can learn.

129
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,298
You don't know a thing,

130
00:06:57,574 --> 00:06:59,200
yet you shamelessly
want to start a club?

131
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,120
Nobody's born knowing everything.

132
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,920
How would I know I can't unless I try?

133
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,640
I'm really curious.

134
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,520
Why do you want to start a club?

135
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,680
I...

136
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,640
I...

137
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,822
Allow me to explain it.

138
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,229
You're doing it for the credits.

139
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,840
For the scholarship, right?

140
00:07:18,258 --> 00:07:19,960
With motives like that,

141
00:07:19,996 --> 00:07:21,240
and no climbing experience,

142
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:23,977
how can I possibly
trust you with the space?

143
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,688
You're just not qualified.

144
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,520
Then tell me,

145
00:07:28,777 --> 00:07:30,422
what would make me qualified?

146
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,000
Come with me.

147
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,000
If you can climb up there,

148
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,622
I'll sign it right away.

149
00:07:59,683 --> 00:08:00,483
Deal.

150
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,840
What now? Planning to skydive?

151
00:08:30,149 --> 00:08:31,545
You can't even put on the gear,

152
00:08:31,770 --> 00:08:33,133
and you want to lead a club?

153
00:08:33,749 --> 00:08:34,890
Just give it up.

154
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,680
Climbing's not as easy as you think.

155
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:39,880
I know it's not easy.

156
00:08:40,425 --> 00:08:41,560
But I'll never give up.

157
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,814
Just don't go back on your word.

158
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,276
If I make it up there,

159
00:08:45,327 --> 00:08:46,163
you have to sign it.

160
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,320
Just a kind reminder.

161
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:53,177
You need proper
climbing shoes for this.

162
00:09:03,911 --> 00:09:06,577
(Palms face down, strike simultaneously.
Arms bent 90° overhead...)

163
00:09:17,755 --> 00:09:18,540
(Climbing Techniques)

164
00:09:51,276 --> 00:09:52,956
Give me a sip of water.

165
00:09:53,066 --> 00:09:55,320
Wait till you reach
the next rock before.

166
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,720
Let me push you a little.

167
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,520
You need to try harder, got it?

168
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,360
You got this!

169
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:02,320
Go, Jian Dan!

170
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,360
Go, Jian Dan!

171
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,440
Jian Dan!

172
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,360
Go, go, go!

173
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,967
You can do it!

174
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,690
Let's go!

175
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,240
Maybe lose some weight
while you're at it!

176
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:15,280
No way!
I love myself just the way I am.

177
00:10:55,756 --> 00:10:56,483
Sheng.

178
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:00,840
You said you wanted
to introduce me to members from

179
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,560
the Swimming Club?

180
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:07,280
Let's go.

181
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,480
Okay.

182
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,472
Come on. Give it a try.

183
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,880
Everyone, come over here!

184
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,880
I have an announcement.

185
00:11:17,138 --> 00:11:18,480
Starting today,

186
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,160
our Swimming Club

187
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:20,680
has a brand-new member.

188
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,280
Introduce yourself.

189
00:11:22,466 --> 00:11:23,511
Give it up for her!

190
00:11:25,261 --> 00:11:27,080
Hi, everyone. I'm Gu Entong.

191
00:11:27,090 --> 00:11:28,600
I'm really happy that starting today,

192
00:11:28,622 --> 00:11:30,040
I get to join the Swimming Club too

193
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,400
and be part of this big family.

194
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:34,000
I'm not quite sure yet

195
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,160
what everyone likes,

196
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,480
so I just brought a bunch of snacks.

197
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:38,920
Hope you all like them.

198
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,120
This is awesome!

199
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:43,440
Please give me a dozen more
new members like her!

200
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,600
Keep dreaming.

201
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:46,320
Entong, did I ever tell you

202
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:48,288
you're the prettiest
and most thoughtful girl

203
00:11:48,311 --> 00:11:49,311
I've ever met?

204
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,189
Whoever ends up dating you

205
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,152
is going to smile in their sleep.

206
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,160
Han Yansheng!

207
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,160
I'm ready.

208
00:12:05,530 --> 00:12:06,505
Alright then. Let's go.

209
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,240
What are those two up to?

210
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:14,320
No point guessing on our own.

211
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,520
Let's go over and see.

212
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,120
I'm not going. I have to work.

213
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,400
I'm off.

214
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:09,520
Han, what's going on
with you and Jian Dan?

215
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:12,520
Why did she suddenly
ask you to watch her climb?

216
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:14,355
She wants to start a Rock Climbing Club.

217
00:13:14,377 --> 00:13:15,844
She needs the second-floor space.

218
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:17,200
We made a deal.

219
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:19,734
If she can climb
to the very top of this wall,

220
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,911
I'll let her use the space.

221
00:13:23,688 --> 00:13:25,333
She wants to start a Rock Climbing Club?

222
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,880
That's ambitious.

223
00:13:40,352 --> 00:13:41,109
Watch this.

224
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:15,160
For a girl, she's doing pretty well.

225
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,080
It's fine. She grabbed on.

226
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:26,311
That was close.

227
00:14:29,680 --> 00:14:30,720
Quick reflexes, huh?

228
00:14:31,111 --> 00:14:32,000
Props to you!

229
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:56,120
Careful!

230
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:56,800
Jian Dan!

231
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:57,280
Be careful!

232
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,588
Come down! It's too dangerous!

233
00:14:58,588 --> 00:15:00,220
- Jian Dan, watch out!
- Hold on tight, Jian Dan!

234
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:01,590
- Don't push yourself!
- Hold steady!

235
00:15:01,680 --> 00:15:03,266
Jian Dan, come down!

236
00:15:04,177 --> 00:15:05,080
Come down, Jian Dan!

237
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:05,640
Careful!

238
00:15:06,461 --> 00:15:07,920
You can step on the right foothold!

239
00:15:07,920 --> 00:15:09,065
Grab it!

240
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:12,680
- Keep going!
- Come on!

241
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:13,619
You got this, Jian Dan!

242
00:15:13,620 --> 00:15:14,920
- Go, Jian Dan!
- You can do it!

243
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:20,440
Right side foothold!

244
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:22,760
To the right!

245
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:25,180
- Nice!
- Good!

246
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,333
- Great job!
- Awesome!

247
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:34,600
You got this!

248
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,066
- Keep going!
- Go for it!

249
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:37,960
You got it!

250
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:39,640
Come on!

251
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:47,860
(Rock Dancer)

252
00:15:50,912 --> 00:15:52,190
- Amazing!
- That was awesome!

253
00:15:52,192 --> 00:15:53,120
Han Yansheng, I did it!

254
00:16:41,280 --> 00:16:41,960
Sheng.

255
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,829
Our club meeting is starting soon.

256
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:44,840
We should hurry.

257
00:16:45,036 --> 00:16:45,734
Alright.

258
00:17:14,512 --> 00:17:15,327
Jian Dan.

259
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,887
You kissed Han Yansheng!

260
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:20,876
Stop it! It was just an accident!

261
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:22,025
An accident?

262
00:17:22,080 --> 00:17:22,880
Look!

263
00:17:22,911 --> 00:17:25,360
(Sheng-Dan Upside-Down Kiss)
You two made campus gossip headlines.

264
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:27,555
You're now number one
on Ocean University's trending list.

265
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:29,440
This is lame.

266
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:33,600
The person who posted it
even added a poll.

267
00:17:33,720 --> 00:17:36,520
Right now, the Tong-Yan ship is
way ahead of the Sheng-Dan ship.

268
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:39,720
Tong-Yan ship and Sheng-Dan ship?

269
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:43,200
Gu Entong and Han Yansheng
are the Tong-Yan ship.

270
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:45,520
You and Han Yansheng
are the Sheng-Dan ship.

271
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:47,680
Netizens are way too insane now.

272
00:17:48,047 --> 00:17:48,920
I'm casting my vote!

273
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:52,680
I'm voting with your phone too.

274
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:55,999
Use your own phone!

275
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,170
- Nope.
- Just give it to me.

276
00:17:57,177 --> 00:17:58,650
We cannot lose to Gu Entong

277
00:17:58,716 --> 00:18:00,956
in popularity, is that clear?

278
